---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Terms of Service" description="Read the Aetas.ai terms of service.">
  <section class="py-24 px-6 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
    <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-display font-bold text-white mb-8">Terms of Service</h1>
    <div class="space-y-6 text-sm text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
      <p>Last updated: July 4, 2026</p>
      <p>By accessing our marketing site at Aetas.ai, you agree to comply with our Terms of Service.</p>
      <h2 class="text-xl font-display font-bold text-white mt-8">1. Acceptable Use</h2>
      <p>You agree not to probe, scan, or test the vulnerability of our website, or attempt to bypass any security gates or login blocks.</p>
      <h2 class="text-xl font-display font-bold text-white mt-8">2. Intellectual Property</h2>
      <p>All trademarks, logos, designs, and content displayed on Aetas.ai are the property of Aetas.ai or their respective owners. Unauthorized use is prohibited.</p>
      <h2 class="text-xl font-display font-bold text-white mt-8">3. Disclaimers</h2>
      <p>Services in our AI pillar are in development. Roadmap claims represent current design objectives, and we do not guarantee specific release dates or features for these pilot programs.</p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
